column2: SELECT TOP # a.specobjID, b.ObjID, c.wise_cntr, d.cntr, p.objID into mydb.MyTable_# from stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust as a LEFT JOIN SpecPhotoAll as b on a.specObjID = b.specObjID LEFT JOIN WISE_xmatch as c on b.ObjID = c.sdss_objid LEFT JOIN WISE_allsky as d on c.wise_cntr = d.cntr LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll as p on b.objID = p.objID ORDER BY b.objID ASC
